OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,FA former pizza delivery driver says he
OL,7,Fis struggling to make ends meet,
OL,8,Fdespite an employment tribunal ruling
OL,9,Fthat he is owed thousands of pounds in
OL,10,Funpaid wages.
OL,12,FIn March, a Jersey court ordered St
OL,13,FHelier business Alvin's Hot Stuff
OL,14,FPizza to pay its ex-employee Jordan
OL,15,FHaynes a total of #3,724 for hours he
OL,16,Fworked since last September and legal
OL,17,Ffines.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,FUnder island law, he should have
OL,7,Freceived the full amount within 14
OL,8,Fdays of the ruling but a month on and
OL,9,Fdespite starting the claim in
OL,10,FNovember, Jordan has still not been
OL,11,Fpaid.
OL,13,FWith the rising cost of living and a
OL,14,Fyoung family to support, he says
OL,15,Fgetting what he is owed by Alvin
OL,16,FAaron's company is crucial.
OL,18,F"I had to say to him I'm going into
OL,19,Fthe children's Income Support money
OL,20,Fbecause we don't have any money left,"
OL,21,FJordan explains.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,F"This is why people go to work, for
OL,7,Fthat security, so we can pay the
OL,8,Fbills, pay the rent, do what we need
OL,9,Fto do but I can't do that if I'm not
OL,10,Freceiving my wages.
OL,12,F"Now, I'm living week by week, day by
OL,13,Fday, as best as we can.
OL,15,F"I'm having to ask family friends to
OL,16,Fborrow money for a one up in school
OL,17,Fclothes because our oldest has had a
OL,18,Fgrowth spurt - I should be able to go
OL,19,Fto my bank account and it say, 'no
OL,20,Fproblem at all'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,F"We've been so strained for money, the
OL,7,Fimpact it's had is huge."
OL,9,FAfter a run of shifts without payment,
OL,10,FJordan says even filling up his car
OL,11,Fwith petrol to do the deliveries
OL,12,Fbecame too expensive so he had to quit.
OL,14,FHowever, Alvin has told ITV News that
OL,15,Fhis pizza delivery firm is struggling
OL,16,Ffinancially, but says he has always
OL,17,Ftreated his workers "like family".
OL,19,FHe disputes the tribunal's findings,
OL,20,Fsaying that despite the legal ruling
OL,21,Fhe does not owe any money to Jordan.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,FIt is not the first time that Alvin
OL,7,Fhas been ordered to pay staff by a
OL,8,Ftribunal.
OL,10,FHis current business is still actively
OL,11,Ftrading, despite its debts.
OL,13,FWhat has become clear from reviewing
OL,14,FJordan's case is there is not one
OL,15,Fsingle body that deals with employment
OL,16,Fdisputes.
OL,18,FYou start with the tribunal which
OL,19,Fmakes a ruling but does not have any
OL,20,Fpower to enforce it.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,FSo if an employer opts not to pay the
OL,7,Fmoney that the court says it owes, as
OL,8,Fin this case, then the worker
OL,9,Fthemselves has to take action by going
OL,10,Fto Petty Debts - a separate legal
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,FThis move means the Viscount can get
OL,14,Finvolved and checks are done to see
OL,15,Fwhat assets the company has.
OL,17,FIf the business cannot pay, it is up
OL,18,Fto the worker again to try and get it
OL,19,Fwound up, effectively starting the
OL,20,Fprocess to shut down the company to
OL,21,Fget some money back as a creditor.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1776888354
OL,3,CEx-delivery driver owed thousands in
OL,4,Cunpaid wages 'living day by day'
OL,6,FThis all takes time and there are
OL,7,Ffurther costs associated with each
OL,8,Fstage, leaving Jordan and others
OL,9,Fasking whether the tribunal process
OL,10,Freally does enough to protect
OL,11,Femployees.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/7
